01:20:03,789 --> 01:20:05,330
And the statement
that it's a fermion

1884
01:20:05,330 --> 01:20:09,310
is the statement that this is
equal to minus psi of b, a.

1885
01:20:09,310 --> 01:20:12,220
If we swap the positions
of the two particles,

1886
01:20:12,220 --> 01:20:14,300
