1892
01:20:27,190 --> 01:20:29,820
So the probability amplitude
to find two fermions

1893
01:20:29,820 --> 01:20:33,390
at the same place is equal to 0.

1894
01:20:33,390 --> 01:20:38,046
Two fermions cannot
