1897
01:20:41,420 --> 01:20:44,800

1898
01:20:44,800 --> 01:20:47,620
Pauli.

1899
01:20:47,620 --> 01:20:49,500
Two.

1900
01:20:49,500 --> 01:20:53,400
If we have-- so this is
