01:21:55,540 --> 01:22:01,410
But psi b of the amplitude to
be at two at the same place

1922
01:22:01,410 --> 01:22:04,500
is equal to-- well, if b
is a, then these two terms

1923
01:22:04,500 --> 01:22:05,930
are identical and
